overview:
The REAL ESTATE PORTAL- REALESTATEKHOJ.COM for all your Property Needs.

Buy, Sell, Rent & Advertise properties online with Real Estate Directory listing Large Data Base of all types of properties city wise & real estate agents with relevant details & contacts.

It provides real estate buyers a database of residential properties & commercial real estate properties with relevant details to browse through, and real estate sellers with a unique space to showcase their property for sell to a wide audience.

Real Estate Khoj- Property website is a platform not only for those who wish to buy or sell real estate property, but also for those who wish to rent/lease any kind of real estate be it agricultural/ residential real estate or commercial property.
Any person can register as an individual or an India real estate agent and avail the services of Real Estate khoj.
